TH SIMPLE_SHELL  "simple shell man page"


.SH NAME
.B Simple Shell
- command interpreter [arguments]

.SH SYNOPSIS
The shell is executed by typing ./hsh

.SH DESCRIPTION
is a command language interpreter that executes commands read from standard input.

.SH OVERVIEW
simple_shell is a command line interpreter that works like the shell


.SH BUILTINS functions

.B pwd
shows the current directory of the process.

.B env
prints the current environment

.B exit
exits the shell

.B help
displays information about builtin commands.

.B history
displays the history list
.SH AUTHOR
Taoufik Jaber.